<parameternamelist>
<parametername>button_id</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The button events to subscribe to. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>delay_ms</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Milliseconds after which &quot;handler&quot; is fired. A value of 0 means to use the system default 500ms. </para>
