</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>up_handler</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The <ref refid="group___clicks_1ga9a923c600f6774d9858ae96b57d308a6" kindref="member">ClickHandler</ref> to fire on the release of a long click. This may be NULL to have no up handler. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
